"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be92d0682b"},{"id":"98492f356a","type":"paragraph","text":"9．“人事科是阎王殿，档案材料是生死薄。”(水58级学生  王金章)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be92d0682b"},{"id":"da0bfbb003","type":"paragraph","text":"10．“共产党想用人时，就把你笼络一下，不用你就把你杀了。”(化59级学生　张君盈)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be92d0682b"},{"id":"47501416d1","type":"paragraph","text":"11．“档案材料是应公开的。”(农60级学生　谭克川)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be92d0682b"},{"id":"29298b86f2","type":"paragraph","text":"12．“档案材料可以在人民内部公开，这只有好处。”(农60级学生　王瑟)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be92d0682b"},{"id":"3ddc30e139","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be92d0682b"}],"page":{"id":"78f7ae5cfb","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be92d0682b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}